s at time 
\begin_inset Formula $k+1$
\end_inset

 and links connecting to the downstream and upstream junctions 
\begin_inset Formula $\jn_{\link}^{\text{Down}}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\jn_{\link}^{\text{Up}}$
\end_inset

 respectively.
 To summarize, 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{x}$
\end_inset

