reference "eq:dx"

\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Using the same line of argument for maximum cardinality in 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{x}$
\end_inset

, we can bound the maximum cardinality of each column of 
\begin_inset Formula $H_{\control}$
\end_inset

.
